Analyze Conversation Transcripts in Data Cloud

To review and analyze conversation data, use Data Cloud to access conversation transcripts from enhanced messaging channels, voice calls, and Unified Messaging. Analyze transcripts in Data Cloud with reports and dashboards, zoom in to your data with Data Cloud API, and search for specific information by using Salesforce Object Query Language (SOQL) queries.

This feature is available only in production.

To enable access to conversation transcripts in Data Cloud:

Verify that Data Cloud is provisioned in your org.
Enable and configure it in Data Cloud Setup.
From Setup, go to Conversation Transcripts in Data Cloud and click Enable.
You can't undo this action.

After enabling, all users with access to the default data space can view and analyze the transcripts from enhanced messaging channels, voice calls, and Unified Messaging.
title: Analyze Conversation Transcripts with Data Cloud
